    <text xml:id="Site_WFY_Section_Bb_Cave42">
        <body>
            <div type="cave" xml:lang="zh">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="bold">42</hi>號窟</head>
                <div>
                    <head>概述</head>
                    <div>
                        <head>位置</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>該窟位於南坡<foreign xml:lang="en">B</foreign>區。</item>
                            <item>
                                <foreign xml:lang="en">f</foreign>壁方向：340°。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>形制</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>疑為方形窟。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>尺寸</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>窟底高於現在的小徑約2米，低於相鄰的<hi rend="bold">41</hi>號窟窟底約80釐米。</item>
                            <item>窟口前部寬度為221釐米。</item>
                            <item>進深：147釐米。</item>
                            <item>高度：167釐米。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>保存狀況</head>
                        <p>石窟未完工，但除了窟後部留有一個石臺、東邊角落尚有一塊巨石外，從窟底至窟頂皆已鑿空。</p>
                        <figure rend="page" n="figure" xml:id="caves_42_41_40_DSC_0111.JPG">
                            <head xml:lang="zh">
                                <hi rend="bold">42</hi>號窟、<hi rend="bold">41</hi>號窟及<hi rend="bold">40</hi>號窟（由左至右）；2010年拍攝</head>
                            <head>Cave <hi rend="bold">42</hi>, next to caves <hi rend="bold">41</hi>, and <hi rend="bold">40</hi>; 
                            photograph taken in 2010</head>
                            <graphic url="caves_42_41_40_DSC_0111.JPG"/>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="cave" xml:lang="en">
                <head type="cave">Cave <hi rend="bold">42</hi>
                </head>
                <div>
                    <head>Description</head>
                    <div>
                        <head>Location</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Southern slope, section B </item>
                            <item>Direction: wall f 340˚</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>Shape</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>intended box shape</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>Measurements</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Height above present walkway: ca. 2 m, ca. 80 cm lower than the floor of neighboring cave <hi rend="bold">41</hi>.</item>
                            <item>Width of opening at front 221 cm</item>
                            <item>Depth: 147 cm</item>
                            <item>Height: 167 cm</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>State of preservation</head>
                        <p>Unfinished cave, but hollowed out from the floor to the ceiling, with the exception of
                        a rock bench at the
                        rear and a block of stone in the eastern corner. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
